# Project Structure Guide

## Directory Organization

### Smart Contract Development
- **Primary Location**: [fhevm-hardhat-template](mdc:fhevm-hardhat-template) - All smart contract development happens here
- **Contracts**: [fhevm-hardhat-template/contracts](mdc:fhevm-hardhat-template/contracts) - Solidity contract files
- **Deployment**: [fhevm-hardhat-template/deploy](mdc:fhevm-hardhat-template/deploy) - Deployment scripts
- **Tests**: [fhevm-hardhat-template/test](mdc:fhevm-hardhat-template/test) - Contract test files
- **Tasks**: [fhevm-hardhat-template/tasks](mdc:fhevm-hardhat-template/tasks) - Hardhat task definitions

### Frontend Development
- **Reference Only**: [frontend](mdc:frontend) - DO NOT MODIFY - Reference implementation only
- **New Projects**: Create new frontend directories at project root level
- **Key Reference Files**:
  - [frontend/fhevm/useFhevm.tsx](mdc:frontend/fhevm/useFhevm.tsx) - FHEVM React hook patterns
  - [frontend/hooks/useFHECounter.tsx](mdc:frontend/hooks/useFHECounter.tsx) - Contract interaction patterns
  - [frontend/components/FHECounterDemo.tsx](mdc:frontend/components/FHECounterDemo.tsx) - UI component patterns

### Configuration Files
- **FHEVM Config**: [fhevm-hardhat-template/hardhat.config.ts](mdc:fhevm-hardhat-template/hardhat.config.ts)
- **Reference**: [Fhevm0.8_Reference.md](mdc:Fhevm0.8_Reference.md) - FHEVM development reference

## Development Workflow
1. Smart contracts → [fhevm-hardhat-template](mdc:fhevm-hardhat-template)
2. Frontend → New root-level directory
3. Reference patterns → [frontend](mdc:frontend) (read-only)
4. FHEVM integration → Follow [frontend/fhevm](mdc:frontend/fhevm) patterns